text: Judy Carne (April 27, 1939 - September 3, 2015) was an English actress. She was best remembered for the phrase "Sock it to me!" on Rowan & Martin's Laugh- In. Carne died in her hometown of Northampton, England on September 3, 2015, after a battle with pneumonia, aged 76. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1939 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Deaths from pneumonia Category:English movie actors Category:English stage actors Category:English television actors Category:Entertainers from Northamptonshire Category:Infectious disease deaths in England Category:People from Northampton
